---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About Shohei Toguchi | Unmuting Ryukyu">

	<!-- HERO -->
	<header style="padding:120px 32px 80px;background:#181818;position:relative;overflow:hidden;border-bottom:1px solid #2a2a3e;">
		<div style="position:absolute;inset:0;background:radial-gradient(circle at 70% 30%, rgba(201,48,44,0.05) 0%, transparent 60%);"></div>
		<div style="position:absolute;right:0;top:-20px;font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif;font-size:300px;font-weight:900;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.02);line-height:1;user-select:none;pointer-events:none;letter-spacing:-0.1em;">ABOUT</div>
		
		<div style="max-width:800px;margin:0 auto;position:relative;z-index:1;">
			<p style="color:#c9302c;font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif;font-size:12px;font-weight:700;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.3em;margin:0 0 24px 0;">The Voice Behind the Silence</p>
			<h1 style="font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif;font-size:clamp(40px,8vw,72px);font-weight:800;color:#f5f0e8;margin:0 0 16px 0;line-height:1;letter-spacing:-0.03em;">Shohei Toguchi</h1>
			<p style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:22px;color:#9ca3af;margin:0;line-height:1.6;max-width:600px;">Documentary filmmaker. Cultural bridge. Performing the soul of Ryukyu for the global stage.</p>
		</div>
	</header>

	<!-- STORY -->
	<section style="padding:100px 32px 140px;background:#181818;">
		<div style="max-width:800px;margin:0 auto;">

			<div style="margin-bottom:100px;">
				<div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:20px;margin-bottom:40px;">
					<div style="width:40px;height:2px;background:#c9302c;"></div>
					<h2 style="font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-weight:700;color:#c8a951;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.2em;margin:0;">The Mission</h2>
				</div>
				<p style="color:#f5f0e8;font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:20px;line-height:1.9;margin:0 0 32px 0;font-weight:300;">
					When I studied in the UK, I realized something painful: the world knows Japan, but almost nobody knows Okinawa. Our language, our music, our history — they were invisible.
				</p>
				<p style="color:#f5f0e8;font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:20px;line-height:1.9;margin:0;border-left:4px solid #c9302c;padding-left:32px;font-style:italic;">
					That's when I decided to dedicate my work to one mission: <strong style="color:#c8a951;font-weight:700;">bringing Okinawa's most precious things to the world through film.</strong>
				</p>
			</div>

			<div style="background:#1a1a2e;border:1px solid #2a2a3e;padding:60px 40px;margin-bottom:100px;position:relative;border-radius:4px;">
				<h3 style="font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif;font-size:32px;font-weight:800;color:#f5f0e8;margin:0 0 24px 0;">Language is Peace</h3>
				<p style="color:#9ca3af;font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:18px;line-height:1.8;margin:0;">
					Learning someone's language is the deepest form of respect. It's not just a skill — it's a peace movement. That's why I work across Japanese, English, Uchinaaguchi, and Mandarin Chinese to bridge cultures that have been separated for too long.
				</p>
			</div>

			<div style="margin-bottom:100px;">
				<div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:20px;margin-bottom:40px;">
					<div style="width:40px;height:2px;background:#c9302c;"></div>
					<h2 style="font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-weight:700;color:#c8a951;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.2em;margin:0;">Capabilities</h2>
				</div>
				<div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(300px,1fr));gap:2px;background:#2a2a3e;border-radius:4px;overflow:hidden;border:1px solid #2a2a3e;">
					<div style="background:#181818;padding:40px;">
						<p style="color:#c9302c;font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:0.15em;text-transform:uppercase;margin:0 0 16px 0;">Communication</p>
						<p style="color:#f5f0e8;font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:15px;line-height:1.8;margin:0;">Japanese, English (TOEIC 955), Uchinaaguchi, Mandarin Chinese. Deep expertise in cross-cultural bridge-building.</p>
					</div>
					<div style="background:#1a1a2e;padding:40px;">
						<p style="color:#c9302c;font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:0.15em;text-transform:uppercase;margin:0 0 16px 0;">Visual Storytelling</p>
						<p style="color:#f5f0e8;font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:15px;line-height:1.8;margin:0;">Documentary production, Premiere Pro, AI-enhanced workflow, and cinematic framing of local narratives.</p>
					</div>
					<div style="background:#1a1a2e;padding:40px;">
						<p style="color:#c9302c;font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:0.15em;text-transform:uppercase;margin:0 0 16px 0;">Cultural Performance</p>
						<p style="color:#f5f0e8;font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:15px;line-height:1.8;margin:0;">Sanshin performance, Eisa, Ryukyuan oral history. Preserving the intangible through performance and archiving.</p>
					</div>
					<div style="background:#181818;padding:40px;">
						<p style="color:#c9302c;font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:0.15em;text-transform:uppercase;margin:0 0 16px 0;">Global Impact</p>
						<p style="color:#f5f0e8;font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:15px;line-height:1.8;margin:0;">Global Shapers (WEF) member, Journal Okinawa Writer, strategist for Okinawan identity in the modern world.</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div style="background:#1a1a2e;border:1px solid #2a2a3e;padding:80px 40px;text-align:center;border-top:4px solid #c9302c;border-radius:4px;">
				<h3 style="font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif;font-size:32px;font-weight:800;color:#f5f0e8;margin:0 0 24px 0;">Let's Redefine the Narrative</h3>
				<p style="color:#9ca3af;font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:18px;margin:0 0 48px 0;line-height:1.8;max-width:600px;margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto;">Whether you need a structural documentary, strategic content, or a bridge to Okinawan culture — I am here to help.</p>
				<div style="display:flex;gap:20px;justify-content:center;flex-wrap:wrap;">
					<a href="/contact/" style="text-decoration:none;background:#c9302c;color:#f5f0e8;font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif;font-weight:700;padding:18px 48px;border-radius:4px;font-size:16px;box-shadow:0 10px 20px rgba(201,48,44,0.3);">Get in Touch</a>
					<a href="https://www.youtube.com/@letsgokinawa" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="text-decoration:none;border:1px solid #2a2a3e;color:#f5f0e8;font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif;font-weight:700;padding:18px 48px;border-radius:4px;font-size:16px;">The Documentaries</a>
				</div>
			</div>

		</div>
	</section>

</Layout>
